The patrician laughed gently. Yes, in a way, but not in the manner you bribed the sergeant  not with a pocket freezer. And even if you reach his scale, it wouldnt be worth it. Theres probably no one so easily bribed, but he lacks even the fundamental honesty of honorable corruption. He doesnt stay bribed; not for any sum. Think of something else.
Devers swung a leg over his knee and his toe nodded quickly and restlessly. Its the first hint, though
