It happened too suddenly for Devers to grasp. It was as if a sudden demon had grown into the old man. Out! said Barr, in a tooth-clenched whisper. Quickly! He seized Rioses dropped blaster and buried it in his blouse.
Sergeant Luk turned as they emerged from the narrowest possible crack of the door.
Barr said easily, Lead on, sergeant!
