Devers said grimly, Hold tight, Barr  and lets see if theyve got a ship that can match my speed.
He knew they hadnt!
And once in open space, the traders voice seemed lost and dead as he said, The line I fed Brodrig was a little too good. It seems as if hes thrown in with the general.
Swiftly they raced into the depths of the star-mass that was the Galaxy.
